subject: Re: Is this group defunct?
msgSnippet: Thanks for checking in with the group! I m still using the alphabet for personal notes and have been doing so for years, though I ve never met anyone else afk
messageBody:
Thanks for checking in with the group! I'm still using the alphabet for personal notes and have been doing so for years, though I've never met anyone else afk who does the same…

They're aren't a lot of messages here nowadays but it's still certainly alive! Feel free to reach out if you think we can help you learn and use the alphabet.

Best,
Quint
